{"tid":1574060,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣令舊貓接受新貓","createTime":"2019-09-16T09:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T06:01:20.000Z","uid":44025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7b99c57150acf9cd946b558201bb84288886df","tid":1574060,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:01:32.000Z","msg":"我半身有隻歲半嘅貓女 琴晚帶咗兩隻幾個月大嘅貓仔返屋企 隻舊貓一見都就係咁恐佢哋 今朝隻舊貓仲喱埋咗 連零食都唔肯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先可能令佢哋雙親相愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LSSknBF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLSSknBF.png&h=1f87cc0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"571152275de5bd170811995ad35b5401770d1b8a","tid":1574060,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBfJ3Kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBfJ3Kt.jpg&h=035c3ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=636a19bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=bbe1e4d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"352bf4e28fc019942db5431ea603878488d5c525","tid":1574060,"uid":107927,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"交換氣味 製造見面機會<br />\n<br />\n貓是對氣味敏感的動物，若直接見面，初五一定會感到威脅，也會為Kumo構成壓力。Luka的破冰第一步，先從氣味開始。「我把牠們的毛巾交換，讓牠們先從氣味認識對方，持續了4、5日。」當兩貓都不抗拒對方的氣味時，就決定讓牠們短暫見面。<br />\n<br />\n第一日，Luka先放新貓出籠走動5分鐘，熟悉新家的環境。然後第二日加長至10分鐘，如此類推，逐日增加。「只放新貓出籠數分鐘，對雙方都有幫助，初五不會覺得地盤被侵佔，Kumo也不會承受過多壓力，當然放貓的時我全程在場觀察着。」只要初五不攻擊新貓，Luka便會賞牠零食。「獎勵比懲罰來得有效，若初五覺得Kumo的存在可以令牠獲得額外食物，會更容易接受新貓。」只需兩星期，兩隻貓已完成破冰儀式，而牠們現在更情同兄弟。「牠們情同手足，連餵藥都會通風報信，先被餵藥的貓會鳴叫，另一隻貓知道了就躲起來。」"},{"pid":"ba5c837a15b73eb4e4750531d31d560109115897","tid":1574060,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5POwmZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5POwmZ.jpg&h=6c778140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZqxX1Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZqxX1Z.jpg&h=69a2c371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hntSX1Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhntSX1Z.jpg&h=8f500fa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wAaKG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wAaKG0.jpg&h=bb793d9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SUbt8F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SUbt8F.jpg&h=9b336ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdQYTAk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdQYTAk.jpg&h=95a429fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHpyHtF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHpyHtF.jpg&h=d7c47293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYA90fm.jpg\" data-thumbna