By":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:38:54.000Z","msg":"我隻舊貓直程喱埋唔肯出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"我果隻相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊貓去到邊就打到邊 你係佢面前經過 佢覺得唔順眼 照開你拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ccdc07ad0e14f46430ebe85fe6523734f249e1","tid":1574060,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"舊貓接受新狗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起晒鋼"},{"pid":"47cc8a2d87bd4e82518f0dfd704714702799a2a7","tid":1574060,"uid":55425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T19:00:01.000Z","msg":"對舊貓好d<br />\n<br />\n好似對港女咁，特登係新貓面前抱住舊貓又攬又錫又俾好野佢食<br />\n<br />\n俾舊貓知道你愛佢多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37459250f7544b66a49239b5479a5171c432eeda","tid":1574060,"uid":36807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"爬過文<br />\n最好新嗰隻困一困籠 或者限制佢空間 （可能淨係俾佢係間房咁）持續一星期左右<br />\n跟住每日增加放佢出嚟嘅時間  慢慢試同舊果隻接觸<br />\n每次食嘢都要比舊嗰隻食先 <br />\n要持續地增加時間 唔好心急等佢哋獨處<br />\n<br />\n然後盡量用嘅嘢都各自自己獨立<br />\n即係飲水食嘢嘅兜 貓砂盆 etc（如果條件許可）<br />\n不過自己冇試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢哋好好相處啦"},{"pid":"6c60c0432b853830ef1dec6cb9f63d03d6489f3b","tid":1574060,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T11:16:52.000Z","msg":"more圖plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c12a1251d32ee7015c1a59a62f52e2a3222f7e","tid":1574060,"uid":92325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"新貓隔離法<br />\n對舊貓要明顯好過對新貓<br />\n比野食個順序都要比左舊貓先<br />\n等佢覺得自己仲係被愛同係大佬"}]}